Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:18.36,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:29.82,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.75,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:47.88,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:56.81,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:01:08.70,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:20.59,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:26.43,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:36.23,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.81,0:01:53.25,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(380,110)}Ep. 37 - Robbers on the Prairie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is getting hot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:39.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Summer has come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:45.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This would be our fourth summer\Nsince we came to Southern Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:57.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:07.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You leg hasn't fully healed yet,\Nso you shouldn't work in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:09.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's too hot for me to stay home doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:10.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My leg is all fine already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:25.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! It's over! It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:28.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, teacher!
Comment: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:42.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, starting tomorrow, I won't be passing through here, for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:49.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And... I wonder if it was this tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:56.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Or was it this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:04:01.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Previously, Lucy found money\Nin the bird nest on the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"What if it'll have money in it again?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:08.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, she was clinging tight\Nto that naive thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was this tree for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:47.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, are you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:00.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Little. I see you're doing well too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:06.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How come you're you riding a carriage today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:09.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. That's cause I came\Nto run some errands in the city hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:11.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you'll have to leave again soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I have some time, but only a bit of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:29.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that was scary. I'm sure it was that bird just now.\NThe one that found the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,None here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:46.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Such a too-good-to-be-true thing\Ncouldn't possibly happen to me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You sure there's no mistake, Adam?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:02.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There's no specified time, but master\Nwill transport the money in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:04.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is he bringing along that stupid bulldog?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:05.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:06.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:10.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That dog will cause trouble.\NWe've gotta do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:11.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:44.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Doctor Deighton!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to our house, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I need to examine your father's leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:54.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you returning from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:55.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:07:00.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing how much you detest going to school, it's admirable how you do it without taking any breaks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:03.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped. But at least\Nwe've vacations starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:03.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Summer vacations, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:08.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? No wonder it's so hot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:12.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, did Mr. Pettywell\Ntell you anything else since the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:13.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,About the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:14.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He sure as heck did. Every day,\Nhe comes to tell me to vacate the house sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, he said I've only four days left\Nuntil one month runs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Pettywell did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't do it himself.\NAlways sends his agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Usually that servant Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:27.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:30.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I saw that man a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He might come to my place today as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:36.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What'll you do if they drive you out of that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you persist in saying you're not going anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:42.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Mr. Pettywell won't hesitate\Nto tear that house down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:48.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think of something.\NThanks for all that concern, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:54.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! A carriage stopped in front of our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:55.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:03.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Little, who came in that carriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:09.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father, I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:12.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to exert yourself just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:13.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I should be fine, doing this little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:17.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mother told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:20.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We no longer have any money in the house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:25.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've not been working for the last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:28.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought there is still some saved up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:32.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You should know the prices\Nhave been growing like mad these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.46,0:08:37.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. So far, I've been taking it easy. From now on,\NI'll be bringing as much money as I can into the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:41.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Up to now, you've already been doing\Nmore than enough for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:45.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Once I can work again, we'll figure something out.\NDon't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But with a leg like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:48.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it still aches a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:51.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, you shouldn't be using it yet, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:55.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:01.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. You're back too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:02.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father, I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:03.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Deighton also came with a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:08.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? This could be very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:11.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready for a lecture from Doctor, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:25.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When do your school vacations start?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can finally play as much as I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:32.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Your nonchalance is one thing that never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, did you come here by carriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:36.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:40.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Since you have vacations starting tomorrow,\Nhow about I give you and Kate a ride to the port?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To the port? I like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The port changed considerably.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:48.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It looks all great and gorgeous now.\NYou've not been there for a while, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:49.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:56.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Return before nightfall, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:57.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:01.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to catch a ride back for them,\Nso don't worry about that, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:06.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, behave and wait patiently!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:09.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How about we depart, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:10.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come home next Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Giddyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:22.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:35.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Silver, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:40.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Adam! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:42.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:48.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Comment: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:50.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:00.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. We can leave now, George.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Giddyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:27.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any kangaroos here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:30.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, have you seen any kangaroos on your way to the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:32.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:36.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even though there are talks about kangaroos\Nswarming this area recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:38.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You think someone could've\Nslaughtered them for their meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:41.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to say something so brutal, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:44.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Beef and pork have been\Nincreasingly expensive recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:48.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, some folk switched to eating the meat\Nfrom kangaroos, sheep, and even opossums.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:50.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop! I don't want to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:53.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we last ate bacon either...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Our family is in a tight spot right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:00.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As a part of our family, you should render\Nany assistance possible to dad and mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:01.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:05.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're shrewd so you probably\Nalready understand the situation, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:07.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:12.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can render assistance as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:13.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:15.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you also counting on me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:18.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're still too little...\NBut I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:22.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not recognizing me as a grown-up was rude of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:24.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For God's sake, Lucy!\NThat's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:27.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! I'm recognize! I recognize you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, seems like a carriage\Nis catching up from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's Mr. Pettywell's carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:42.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pettywell's?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:44.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Giddyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:49.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We can by no means lose to him, Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:52.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I get it. Hang on tight, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:52.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:53.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Giddyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Giddyup! Giddyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:14.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Giddyup! Giddyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Giddyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose to Mr. Pettywell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,George, strike the horse more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Already did, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:34.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Do it more! More!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:37.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Giddyup! Giddyup! Hey-ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:42.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Giddyup! Giddyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:43.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:45.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:50.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. If we spur it any further,\Nthe horse will collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:51.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:52.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:55.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Keep such lousy things out of your mouth, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:58.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you said it multiple times just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that... I'm a man, so it's alright for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:05.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... Frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:10.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:25.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We can play around for two more hours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:27.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, come back to here when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to the stagecoach station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:33.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Kate, let's go to the end of that embankment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:34.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:41.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Lucy!
Comment: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:45.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:48.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:51.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:15:01.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The port was nothing like what it's been\Nby the time of our arrival three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:09.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Lucy?\NI don't want to see any bugs again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:11.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:13.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's a seashell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:30.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Kate. It wasn't this place\Nwhere we disembarked, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:31.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was more to the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:36.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how when we first set foot on the ground,\Nwe repeated after dad and thump-thumped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alley-hop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:51.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:07.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This is the land where we'll spend the rest of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:09.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Comment: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:12.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Feels so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:22.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're in Australia!\NWe're in Australia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:25.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot all about it.\NDid we really do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:26.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:30.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When we first disembarked,\Nwe still had a hope burning bright in us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:34.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,that we'll get the land straightaway,\Nand build an enormous farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:38.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That hope left for somewhere else now, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:40.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:55.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Without hope, everything is lost, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:55.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:26.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's best that you stop at that, Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:29.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose drinking is bad for my leg, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:34.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to alcohol, I can't speak too harshly about it, but still, too much of it won't do anyone good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:37.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't drink a cup or two,\NI might be unable to take it, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you can get right back to work\Nonce your leg heals up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:44.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Save for continuing to work at that godforsaken place,\Nmy prospect for future are less than bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:46.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just give it some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:49.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I've been telling myself until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:55.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If you give way to despair,\Nwhat do you think will become of your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:59.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You sure like eating well, Marsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My family...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:06.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:14.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:17.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:20.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wish we could play by the sea for longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We should've gone fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:34.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We should've gone swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:37.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, all we gained was this seashell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:39.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Really, that's a beautiful one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:40.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you still haven't fixed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:48.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:50.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry the damn up! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:58.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Master! A stagecoach is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:02.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can return to Adelaide on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like you can fix it\Nany time soon, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:07.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Terribly sorry for the delay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:08.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:11.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Adam, what will we do about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose they'll let him into the stagecoach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:16.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanted to return today,\Ntogether with him and the bag. Today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll ride with you,\Nso don't worry about the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't strike me as all that reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, go stop that stagecoach for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:27.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:30.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:32.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:36.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, we're in a bit of a trouble.\NBut Master would like to return to Adelaide sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:38.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:41.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Toss your bag on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.73,0:19:43.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, we'd rather keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:48.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Giddyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.40,0:19:54.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:57.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, if it isn't Mr. Popple's daughters?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Mr. Pettywell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:01.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:05.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, your carriage was completely unable\Nto keep up with mine, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:08.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems, yours broke down as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:08.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:11.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Giddyup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:52.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's a robber!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:55.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:57.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:03.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're the robbers! Everyone out!
Comment: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:04.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:06.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:09.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They're robbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:10.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Robbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Make it quick before I killed everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Get off faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.06,0:21:21.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:23.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You get off too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:36.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you people come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, start walking, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:46.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:47.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be alright, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:22:01.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Collect everyone's\Nmoney and valuables into this bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:04.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:09.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We're short on hands here,\Nso I need your help with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:11.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But if you keep being uncooperative...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! No! I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:17.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good, that's what I like to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.45,0:22:21.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, begin by putting your money\Nand that ring into the sack.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:22.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:27.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You still have more money on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:29.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,N-no, I absolutely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:30.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:32.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And what's this called?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:34.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:36.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:40.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You get it? Get all your money\Nand valuables out, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:42.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, get up and collect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:53.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The way you've been clutching onto this bag\Nsuggests there's something important in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:53.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:54.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:22:57.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Give it here at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:22:58.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:22:59.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you value your life at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:01.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Here.
Comment: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:03.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:09.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Not that! That, I definitely can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:10.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get back to the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:11.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:13.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need your life or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.61,0:23:15.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give it up!\NI'm never giving it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:18.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Master, think about your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.05,0:23:24.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There's no specified time,\Nbut master will transport money in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:26.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure there's no mistake, Adam?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:28.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is he bringing along that stupid bulldog?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:29.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Comment: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:32.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:39.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Move away from there!\NOr else you'll lose both the bag and your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.40,0:23:40.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:43.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you have until I count to ten to move away...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:45.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.91,0:23:47.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.15,0:23:48.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a method of threatening!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:48.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:49.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:49.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.41,0:23:51.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:54.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,"What exactly is it that Lucy is so afraid of?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:53.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.51,0:23:54.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:56.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I didn't know the answer yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:56.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.52,0:23:57.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:23:59.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:06.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I know who was the robbers' accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.26,0:24:08.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But the guys in police wouldn't believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.80,0:24:11.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I should do what I can to catch them myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.35,0:24:15.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Lucy-May of the Southern Rainbow:\N"Lucy, the Detective".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.19,0:24:16.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
